	quest.1B67CDAA9F6BB7B6.title: "The End is gone, again"
	quest.2139B0C91B4164A1.quest_desc: [
		"You can now cobble together your first Andesite frames, while moderately costly, they're mostly made of basic rocks and plants you gathered in your local environment."
		""
		"Once you unlock brass these casings will become much cheaper, so we should start to work towards the next step to reaching brass. Unlocking the Nether!"
	]
	quest.2139B0C91B4164A1.quest_subtitle: "The End of the Tutorial"
	quest.2139B0C91B4164A1.title: "Onward Heros!"
	quest.21991E4C2F1168A5.quest_desc: [
		"Can be used alongside packagers to expand your stock link connection network and semi-automate many things. "
		""
		"Eventually Factory Gauges will allow high logistics automation of many components."
		""
		""
		"With this, the amount of automation expectations and their complexity will increase through the brass and steel Canto's"
	]
	quest.21991E4C2F1168A5.quest_subtitle: "A Packagers Best Friend"
